<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٤٥ - <span class="c2">«ابنا العاص مؤمنان: هشام وعمرو»</span> .<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
